================================================================================
  PRIORITY 1 — CRITICAL / BLOCKING 
================================================================================

[ ] RUN END-TO-END TEST WITH LIVE MODES
    Confirm POST /assess completes with CSPR_CLOUD_MODE=live + AURUM_DEPLOY_MODE=live
    against a real testnet wallet and a tx_hash is returned.
    File: api/test_scripts/test_e2e.py
    Check: tx_hash is a real 64-char hex, not "mock-deploy-..."

[ ] FIX issue_credit_score DUPLICATE DEPLOY PROTECTION
    The CreditRegistry contract rejects issue_credit_score if a credential
    already exists for the borrower (CredentialAlreadyExists error).
    Attestation agent needs to check Supabase first and call update_score
    instead of issue_credit_score when a record already exists.
    File: api/agents/attestation_agent.py

[ ] VERIFY caller ARG IN ATTESTATION AGENT DEPLOY
    The deployed Odra contract entrypoints take a "caller" string as the
    first argument. The attestation agent calls submitter.submit_contract_call()
    directly and must include "caller": CASPER_ACCOUNT_HASH in its args dict.
    Confirm this is present — if missing, every live deploy will fail silently.
    File: api/agents/attestation_agent.py

[ ] BUILD FRONTEND (web/)
    web/ is a default Next.js skeleton. Nothing is connected to the API.
    Minimum viable UI:
      - Wallet address input field
      - POST /assess button -> display score, tier, tx_hash
      - GET /oracle/query section with payment proof input
    File: web/app/page.tsx


================================================================================
  PRIORITY 2 — HIGH  
================================================================================

[ ] DEFI SCORING DIMENSIONS — LIVE DATA
    defi, rwa, dao, repayment dimensions always score 0 in live mode because
    CSPR.cloud testnet has no DeFi endpoints confirmed yet.
    When endpoints become available, wire them into cspr_cloud/defi.py.
    File: api/cspr_cloud/defi.py
    Current fallback: empty lists -> score 0 for all four dimensions

[ ] X402 SIGNATURE VALIDATION
    The payment proof includes a "signature" field that is never validated.
    In live mode the on-chain transfer scan is the only guard.
    For production: verify the payer signed the proof with their Ed25519 key.
    File: api/casper/x402.py  ->  X402Verifier.verify()

[ ] X402 NONCE PERSISTENCE
    Nonces are stored in a Python in-memory set(). Server restart clears
    replay protection entirely. A replayed proof within the same nonce window
    will be accepted after restart.
    Fix: persist consumed nonces in Supabase with a TTL.
    File: api/casper/x402.py  ->  X402Verifier._used_nonces

[ ] SWITCH X402_MODE TO LIVE
    X402_MODE=mock is currently set in api/.env.
    Change to live once a real CSPR payment test passes.
    File: api/.env

[ ] DEPLOY API TO PUBLIC HOST
    API is only accessible at localhost:8000.
    Deploy to Render / Railway / VPS.
    Update CORS origins in api/main.py to match the deployed domain.
    File: api/main.py  ->  origins list


================================================================================
  PRIORITY 3 — MEDIUM  
================================================================================

[ ] HANDLE call_getter() GAS COST AND LATENCY
    call_getter() submits a real put-deploy and polls up to 60 seconds.
    For high-read endpoints (oracle history, compliance checks), this is too slow.
    Options:
      a. Cache chain reads in Supabase with a TTL (preferred)
      b. Add a read-only RPC method if Casper SDK exposes one
    Files: api/casper/deploy_submitter.py, api/routers/oracle.py

[ ] ADD /assess REQUEST VALIDATION
    POST /assess currently accepts any dict. Add:
      - wallet_address required and non-empty
      - format validation (hex string, length check)
      - rate limiting per IP
    File: api/routers/assess.py

[ ] ADD CRON MONITOR AUTHENTICATION
    POST /cron/monitor is publicly accessible with no auth.
    Add a secret header check (CRON_SECRET env var) before processing.
    File: api/routers/cron.py

[ ] FIX get_cspr_balance() STUB IN client.py
    CasperClient.get_cspr_balance() returns a TODO dict.
    Not currently used in production paths but should be wired to
    query-balance via casper-client CLI.
    File: api/casper/client.py

[ ] STALE AGENTS/docs/AGENT_PIPELINE LOCATION
    The AGENT_PIPELINE doc is at api/agents/docs/AGENT_PIPELINE.
    The WORKFLOW and TODO docs are at api/docs/.
    Consolidate all docs under api/docs/ for consistency.


================================================================================
  PRIORITY 4 — LOW: Production
================================================================================

[ ] PER-AGENT KEY ENFORCEMENT
    All contract calls currently use the deployer key (CASPER_ACCOUNT_HASH).
    Keys are generated (keys/ directory exists) but contracts only accept
    calls from the deployer account. Requires a contract upgrade on mainnet
    to assign per-agent roles via assign_role().
    Files: api/agents/attestation_agent.py, contracts/credit_registry/src/lib.rs

[ ] SEPARATE KEYS PER AGENT FOR LLM CALLS
    All Groq calls currently share 2 keys. For production rate limits,
    generate one key per agent.

[ ] IPFS ATTESTATION STORAGE
    attestation_hash is currently a Supabase URL.
    For true decentralization, pin the attestation JSON to IPFS and store
    the IPFS CID as the on-chain attestation_hash.
    File: api/agents/attestation_agent.py, api/db/supabase.py

[ ] REAL DEFI PROTOCOL INTEGRATIONS
    Lending pool offers (TrueFi, Maple, Clearpool) are hardcoded.
    Integrate real rate feeds and pool availability APIs.
    File: api/agents/lending_agent.py

[ ] DAO SCORING — REAL GOVERNANCE DATA
    dao dimension uses yield events as a proxy.
    Real DAO vote data requires a governance indexer not yet available
    on CSPR.cloud. Track when this endpoint ships.
    File: api/cspr_cloud/defi.py  ->  get_yield_events()

[ ] CASPER V2 CONTRACT MIGRATION
    Contracts are Odra v1 (hash- prefix, put-deploy path).
    Casper v5 client deprecated put-deploy in favor of put-transaction
    with invocable-entity for v2 entity addresses.
    When upgrading contracts to Casper v2, update deploy_submitter.py.
    File: api/casper/deploy_submitter.py  ->  submit_contract_call()

[ ] ADD ASYNC PIPELINE EXECUTION
    pipeline.invoke() is synchronous and blocks the FastAPI event loop.
    Wrap in asyncio.run_in_executor() or move to a background task queue
    (Celery / ARQ) and return a job_id with a polling endpoint.
    File: api/routers/assess.py

[ ] MONITORING AGENT — PROACTIVE ALERTS
    Currently monitoring only runs during POST /cron/monitor re-scoring.
    Add a notification path: when monitoring_action="revoke", send an
    alert (email / webhook) to the wallet owner or admin.
    File: api/agents/monitoring_agent.py, api/routers/cron.py

[ ] ORACLE QUERY — SCORE HISTORY ENDPOINT
    GET /oracle/history returns only one record (most recent).
    Supabase query should return all records ordered by created_at desc.
    File: api/routers/oracle.py  ->  query_credit_history()

[ ] SCORING MODEL — RETRAIN ON REAL DATA
    XGBoost model is trained on synthetic wallet profiles.
    Once real CSPR.cloud DeFi data is available, retrain and evaluate.
    File: api/scoring/model.py, api/scoring/train.py (if it exists)


